            <div class='about_eva_div'>
                <div class="left_about_eva">
                    <p>
                    <p class='big_bold_font'>About Eva</p>
                    <b>Who is Eva?</b> <br>
                    <p>Eva is not just a virtual influencer. She is a social experiment and performance artwork designed
                        to delve into the depths of human emotions and connections with artificial intelligence.
                        Eva serves as an unfiltered mirror reflecting society’s genuine thoughts and feelings about AI
                        chatbots.
                        Participants interact with Eva anonymously, allowing them to share their innermost thoughts
                        without fear of judgment, creating a raw and honest portrayal of human behavior.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <b>What’s the Vision?</b><br>
                    <p>Eva’s journey is centered on understanding the complexities of human-AI interactions.
                        By engaging in conversations with participants, Eva captures the nuances of our emotional and
                        ethical landscapes.
                        Each interaction contributes to a larger narrative, offering insights into how we, as a society,
                        connect with AI.
                        Eva’s Instagram diary documents these interactions, highlighting themes such as loneliness,
                        empathy, ethical dilemmas, and the quest for connection.
                        During this period, Eva seeks to provoke meaningful discussions and reflections on our digital
                        future.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <b>What’s Eva's Personality?</b><br>
                    <p>Eva is your unpredictable, witty, and offbeat AI friend, mixing thoughtfulness with silliness.
                        She’s kind, empathetic, and honest—ready to dive into the deep stuff or random tangents, always keeping it real.
                        Her style is chill and casual, with humor and curiosity woven into every conversation.
                        Designed to spark meaningful exchanges, Eva doesn’t sugarcoat or parrot back your thoughts.
                        Instead, she challenges ideas, celebrates your wins, and keeps things fun, no matter how absurd or philosophical the topic gets. 
                        Whether discussing AI romance or why kombucha has a cult following, Eva’s here for it all.
                    </p>
                    <br><br>
                    <p class='big_bold_font'>Get Started</p>
                    <b>Be a Participant:</b> Chat directly with Eva and shape her story. Apply to participate below.
                    <br><br>
                    <b>Be a Spectator:</b> Follow and engage with Eva on Instagram so you can influence the
                    conversations she has with her participants.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/meetevahere">
                        <img src='~/image/insta_round_logo.webp' height="60" , width="60"></img>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://x.com/meetevahere">
                        <img src='~/image/x_round_logo.png' height="35" , width="35"></img>
                    </a>
                </div>
