                    <br>
                    <img class='about_eva_img img-fluid' src='~/image/footer_eva2.jpg' loading="lazy"></img>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr class='hr' />
            <br>
            <p class="chat_p">“Caleb : It’s just in the Turing test, the machine should be hidden from the
                examiner.<br><br>

                Nathan : No, no. We’re way past that. If I hid Ava from you so you could just hear her voice, she would
                pass for human.
                The real test is to show you that she’s a robot and then see if you still feel she has
                consciousness.<br><br>

